WEBVTT

00:04.080 --> 00:05.920
Hey, Mrs. Forman.
Hey, Red.

00:06.000 --> 00:09.400
Hello, boys.
You're up bright and early this morning.

00:09.480 --> 00:11.320
Yeah.
We're going to Funland!

00:11.400 --> 00:13.840
It's super fun!

00:13.880 --> 00:17.040
Oh, Red, remember how we used
to take Eric there when he was little?

00:17.120 --> 00:19.800
Remember how I used to get on
the roller-coaster with him...

00:19.880 --> 00:23.120
and then, just before we took off,
I'd jump out and wave good-bye?

00:24.920 --> 00:26.840
Boy, did he scream.

00:27.800 --> 00:29.600
Well, it sounds like fun.

00:29.680 --> 00:31.520
Super fun!

00:31.600 --> 00:34.840
And we figured Eric could use some fun,
you know, since he and Donna broke up.

00:34.880 --> 00:36.840
- What?
- Broke up?

00:36.920 --> 00:39.720
Yeah, I heard Donna
dumped his ass.

00:39.800 --> 00:42.320
That's funny.
I heard Eric was the one who dumped Donna.

00:42.360 --> 00:45.760
- Sure, he did.
- Yeah, right.

00:45.840 --> 00:48.440
Well, Eric must be just a wreck.

